data.description: Come home to this beautiful one story home featuring lots of space to entertain.   Two primary suites are great for generational living.  Formal living and formal dining.  Family room features a wood burning fireplace and beamed ceiling. Kitchen has beautiful cabinetry, granite counters and stainless appliances. Owner's suite has ensuite bath, dressing area and two walk in closets.  Second primary bedroom with ensuite bath has a large shower and is wheel chair accessible. Two secondary bedrooms both have lots of closet space. French doors from the dining room lead you to the backyard oasis. Great for entertaining, the large, covered patio can accommodate a sitting are and dining area. The pool is large enough for family and friends to enjoy. Beautifully landscaped, there are lots of low maintenance flowering plants. An extra bonus is the garden shed for tools and supplies. Convenient to stores and shopping. Easy commuting.  Zoned to highly rated Klein Schools.  Come see this one today!
